Definition predk k := preim key (pred1 k).

Structure finMap : Type := FinMap { seq_of : seq (K * V); _ : sorted ord (map key seq_of)}.

Definition fnd k (s : fmap) := if (filter (predk k) (seq_of s)) is (_, v):: _ then Some v else None.
